# Marauder WebSerial module

- Serial writes go through `SerialClient.write()` / `sendCommand()` only from user actions.
- Port wardrive parsing logic from Vue (`wardriveParser.js`) — do not mix with LilyGO `serial_parser.dart`.
- Use `device_source=pwnterrey marauder` for platform upload.
- Document protocol changes in `docs/marauder_ui_pro_logic.md`.
- After edits: `dart format .`, `dart analyze`, `flutter test`.
